              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Взрыв стихии</span></p><p>Наносит <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Пиро урон</span>, 6 ед.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/70239714/5779f79888d140f222ce693c329228d8_126837528620660422.png",
                "id": "talent37232",
                "key": "Кружащийся блеск",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
